    <h3>Community Information</h3>
    <p>A part of the Kansas City Metropolitan Area, in the "Heart of America", Shawnee Mission is comprised of independent, suburban cities.  Local parks, that include swimming pools for the public and fields for outdoor games and activities, can be found all over.  With a small-town feel, there are still many varied shopping areas.  Only a few miles from Kansas City, Shawnee Mission is perfect for any student who wants to be close to the big city.  With a thriving culture evident everywhere in Kansas City, there are places for music, opera, dance and theater.  Different performance centers are open to explore, as well amusement parks and shopping areas.  With something for all styles, there is guaranteed to be a shop or boutique that caters to everyone.  The most famous shopping and entertainment district, the Country Club Plaza, offers many different ethnic foods and over 100 shops and businesses.  Different museums, libraries, waterparks and historic sites can be found throughout the multiple districts of Kansas City.  There's so much to experience in Shawnee Mission - make it the destination for your cultural exchange!</p>
